  "description": {
    "S": "Make the ultimate Chicken and Dumplings from scratch with this foolproof recipe that features soft, fluffy homemade dumplings in a creamy chicken soup with vegetables. This cozy one-pot meal is perfect for cold winter nights and uses simple pantry ingredients to create the kind of soul-warming comfort food that brings the whole family to the table."
  },
